data.description: Welcome Home to this 3/4 Bedroom Rambler in the Fern Hill Community! This uniques home offers plenty of natural lighting throughout.  3 BR, 1.75 BA with an additional bonus room that could be a 4th BR or game room.  All new appliances. Open floor concept, great for entertaining.  Unfinished covered room attached to home w/ wood stove that leads to the manicured back yard. Fully fenced backyard w/ covered gazebo.  Central A/C and Trane Clean Effects Air Cleaner. Upgraded main bathroom with Heated Flooring/ newly installed bidet toilet- never used. Freshly painted interior throughout. Hardwood floors in bedrooms. Centrally located in South Tacoma- close to freeways, shopping, and JBLM.  A must see to appreciate all the additions to this home.
